FBIS3-17180 "drsov057_b_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Shokhin Appointed Deputy Prime Minister LD2403081994 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0727 GMT 24 Mar 94 LD2403081994 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Ivan Ivanov] [Text] Moscow, 24 Mar -- By decree of the Russian Federation president, Aleksandr Shokhin has been appointed deputy prime minister of the Government. Viktor Chernomyrdin reported this today at the sitting of the Presidium of the Russian Federation Government. The new deputy prime minister will supervise the block of economic issues.
